ingredients: ½ cup of shredded mozzarella cheese
4 large of hard-boiled eggs, peeled and halved
1 (4 ounce) package of white anchovies, washed
1 (15.25 ounce) package of moist white cake mix
2 cups cooked, shredded of chicken meat
3 tablespoons of Borden Cheddar and Monterey Jack Shreds, for topping
8 frozen of hash brown patties, or to taste
2 tubes of refrigerated cinnamon rolls, with icing
½ teaspoon of freshly grated nutmeg
2 pieces of milk chocolate candy bars
¼ teaspoon of garlic salt or 1/4 teaspoon of seasoning salt
½ ounces of simple syrup (one part sugar, one part water)
